nodes.text: Viper was a EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate belonging to the Rebel Alliance. The frigate had, along with several other rebel starships were part of a military summit located at the Delfii system. The ship was for some reason needing new engines which were delivered by the CR90 corvette Deep. Her cargo was warheads.
